OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDesmond Tutu - the staunch 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fand steadfast healer of a  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fnation                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Desmond Tutu is remembered with so much
OL,6, joy and affection by so many different 
OL,7, people around the world today, that it 
OL,8, may seem hard to imagine a time or     
OL,9, place when he was viewed, not as a     
OL,10, courageous moral crusader, but as a    
OL,11, devil.                                 
OL,13,FIt was the mid-1970s, and South Africa 
OL,14,Fwas ruled by a white-minority regime   
OL,15,Fthrough a brutal system of racial      
OL,16,Fapartheid. Nelson Mandela was in prison
OL,17,Fand his Soviet-backed liberation       
OL,18,Fmovement, the ANC, was outlawed.       
